{"title": "Authentication", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "ssh-protocol/authentication", "html": "<h1 id=\"authentication\">Authentication</h1>\n<h4 id=\"testing-credentials\">Testing credentials</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ssh<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;PASSWORD&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Expected Results:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>SSH<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1<span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>SSH-2.0-OpenSSH_8.2p1<span class=\"w\"> </span>Debian-4\nSSH<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1<span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"m\">22</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">127</span>.0.0.1<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>user:password\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"specify-ports\">Specify Ports</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ssh<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--port<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2222</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Authentication Testing credentials nxc ssh &lt;CIDR&gt; -u &lt;USERNAME&gt; -p &lt;PASSWORD&gt; Expected Results: SSH 127 .0.0.1 22 127 .0.0.1 [ * ] SSH-2.0-OpenSSH_8.2p1 Debian-4 SSH 127 .0.0.1 22 12", "tags": []}